This virtual suite runs COEP: credentialless.
With:
 - CrossOriginEmbedderPolicyCredentiallessOriginTrial
Without:
 - CrossOriginEmbedderPolicyCredentialless
 - PlzServiceWorker
 - PlzDedicatedWorker
 - CoepForSharedWorker

Goal is to check the OriginTrial can enable on every context
COEP:credentialless.
